          "license": ""
        },
        "description": {
          "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>The mere sight of the pùca is a temptation for road-weary travelers. Whenever a creature that can see the pùca starts its turn within 30 feet of the pùca, that creature succeed on make a [[/save ability=wisdom dc=15]] saving throw or be &amp;Reference[condition=charmed] for 1 minute. A &amp;Reference[condition=charmed] creature must take the @action[Dash] action and move toward the pùca by the safest available route on each of its turns, trying to get within 5 feet of the fey horse to mount it. Each time the creature takes damage and at the end of each of its turns, the creature can repeat the saving throw, ending the effect on itself on a success. If a creature's saving throw is successful or the effect ends for it, the creature is immune to the pùca's Beguiling Aura for the next 24 hours.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>",
